4D41D27F.VoiceDir15.121C9F: Slightly humorous. Bodies that aren't burned turned into zombies or drowned

8ED7735D.Line1.121C9F: Ah, it's good to see you again! Yes, I am as safe as can be expected in these swamps. I was barely able to give the crusaders proper rites before the bodies began to turn.

F6462D12.Line15.121C9F: It was fortunate that I remembered what my friend, Zrinka, said about burning bodies. I think Akarat would forgive me for not abiding by all of the proper rituals.
